hadiths[168]{hadithnumber,text}:
3970,Hazrat Zohri sey marwi hai ke jin do ghulamon ney aapas mein shirkat mufawiza kar rakhi ho aur un mein sey eik apney aaqa sey azadi ka muahida karey to doosra bhi uski taraf sey adaegi kerega.
3971,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main mushrekin sey ladaai karun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi sacha mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. jab wo gawahi den ke Allah key siwa koi bar-haq mabood nahin aur Muhammad Allah key bandey aur Rasool hain, neez wo hamari tarah namaz padhein aur hamarey qibley ki taraf (doran namaz mein) munh karen aur hamara zibeh kya huwa janwer khaeyn, to uskey baad unkey jaan o maal hum par haram ho jatey hain illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho."
3972,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain. jab wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh keren, hamara zibeh shuda janwer khaeyn aur hamari tarah namaz padhein to hum par unkey jaan o maal haram ho jatey hain, illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho. in ko wo huquq hasil hongey jo musalmanon ko hasil hotey hain aur un par wo faraaiz laagu hongey jo musalmanon par laagu hotey hain."
3973,"Hazrat memnon bin siyah ney Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : abu Hamza ! musalman ki jaan o maal ko kon si chiz qabil ehtiraam banati hai? aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs gawahi dey ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain, hamarey qibley ki taraf munh kerey. hamari tarah namaz padhey aur hamara zibeh shuda janwer khaye , wo musalman hai. us ko musalmanon waley tamam huquq hasil hongey aur is par musalmanon waley tamam faraaiz laagu hongey."
3974,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala ko piyarey ho gaey to bahut sey Arab murtad ho gaey. (Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey ladney ka azm farmaya to) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey abu-Bakar ! aap un Arbon sey kaisey ladengey ? Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah Taala ka Rasool hun, namaz qaaim karen aur Zakat ada karen. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey bakri ka eik bacha na den jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is bina par un sey zarur ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab mainey achchi tarah ghor kya to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki raey hi wazeh aur bar-haq hai."
3975,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah ko piyarey ho gaey aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa banaey gaey aur baaz Arab ( dobara ) kafir ban gaey (aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey ladaai karney ka azm farmaya ) to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap un logon sey kaisey lad saktey hain jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : mujhey logon sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah … الخ » padh lein. jis shakhs ney kalma « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh liya, us ney mujh sey apna maal o jaan mehfooz kar liya illa ye ke uskey zimmey ( Islam ka) koi haq banta ho aur us ka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey : Allah ki qism ! main un logon sey zarur ladun ga jinhoney namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq kar di hai kyonkey Zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey eik rassi deney sey inkar karen jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is par bhi un sey zarur ladun ga. Hazrat umr ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! meri samajh mein aa gaya ke ladaai key liye Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina Allah Taala ney khola hai aur mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke yehi baat bar-haq hai."
3976,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein . jab wo ye kalma padh lein to unhoney mujh sey apna jaan o maal bacha liya, illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq ho aur unka ( andruni ) hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. jab irtidad (Islam sey phirney) ka fitna barpa huwa to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha ke aap un sey ladengey ? jabkey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko yun yun farmatey suna hai. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq nahin karney dunga, balke jo tafriq kerega, main us sey zarur ladunga. (Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : ) phir hamney Hazrat abu-Bakar key sath mil kar ( munkereen Zakat sey) ladaai ki aur usey durust maslak paya. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Zohri ki baabat Sufiyan qawi nahin. (matlab ye ke Sufiyan Zohri sey jo riwayat bayan karta hai wo zaeef hoti hai.) aur ye Sufiyan bin Husein hai."
3977,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey logon sey ladaai karney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah … » padh lein. jis shakhs ney « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh liya, us ney mujh sey apni jaan o maal bacha liye illa ye ke is par Islam ka koi haq banta ho aur us ka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Shuaib bin abu-Hamza ney (mazkura baala ) dono hi riwaayaton (3976, 3977) ko ( do mukhtalif sanadon sey) jama kya hai."
3978,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap key baad khalifa baney aur baaz Arab kafir ban gaey, to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey abu-Bakar ! aap logon sey kaisey ladaai kerengey jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey logon sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein . jis shakhs ney kalma « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh liya, us ney mujh sey apna maal o jaan bacha liya, illa ye ke is par (Islam ka) koi haq banta ho aur us ka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main har us shakhs sey zarur ladunga jo namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq kerega. Zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qasam! agar wo mujhey bakri ka eik bacha bhi deney sey inkar karen jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is wajeh sey un sey ladaai karunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mujhey samajh aa gaee ke Allah Taala ney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina ladaai key liye khol diya hai, neez mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke yehi baat bar-haq hai."
3979,"Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey manqul hai ke unhen saiyedna Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main un logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein . jo shakhs ye kalma padh ley, us ney mujh sey apni jaan o maal ko mehfooz kar liya illa ye ke is par ( Islam ka) koi haq ho, aur us ka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. waleed bin Muslim ney us ( Usman ) ki mukhalifat ki hai."
3980,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney un ( munkireene-zakat) sey ladaai karney ka pukhta faisla kar liya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : aey abu-Bakar! aap un logon sey kaisey lad saktey hain jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo «la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein? jab wo ye kalma padh lengey to mujh sey apney khoon o maal bacha leingey illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main us shakhs sey zarur ladunga jo namaz aur Zakat mein tafriq kerega. Allah ki qism ! agar wo mujhey bakri ka eik bacha bhi nahin dengey jo wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko diya kartey they to main is par un sey ladunga. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! meri samajh mein aa gaya ke Allah Taala ney Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina ladaai key liye khol diya hai aur mainey jaan liya ke yehi baat bar-haq hai.
3981,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladaai ladun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » keh den. jab wo ye keh dengey to mujh sey apney khoon o maal mehfooz kar leingey illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho. aur unka hisab Allah azz-w-jall key zimmey hai.
3982,Hazrat Jabir aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladaai karun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » keh den. jab wo ye kalma padh leingey to mujh sey apney khoon o maal bacha leingey illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho aur unka hisab Allah Taala key zimmey hai.
3983,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum logon sey ladengey yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein . jab wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh leingey to hum par unkey khoon aur maal haram ho jaeyngey illa ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho. baqi raha unka andruni hisab to wo Allah Taala key zimmey hai.
3984,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke hum Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas bethey they ke eik aadmi aap key paas aaya aur us ney aap sey khufiya taur par baat cheet ki. aap ney puchha : usey qatl kar do. phir aap ney farmaya : kya wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » ki gawahi deta hai? us shakhs ney kaha : ji han, lekin wo jaan bachaney key liye kalma padhta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir usey qatl na karo kyonkey mujhey us waqt tak logon sey ladney ki ijazat hai jab tak wo kalma na padh lein. agar wo ye kalma padh lein to unhoney apney khoon o maal mujh sey mehfooz kar liye illa ye ke un par Islam ka haq banta ho. unka hisab Allah Taala par hai."
3985,"Hazrat Noman bin Salim eik sahabi sey bayan kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaney lagey, jabkey hum Madina Munawra ki masjid key quba mein they : mujhey wahi ki gaee hai ke main logon sey ladaai karun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » keh den. baqi riwayat sabiqa riwayat ki tarah hai."
3986,"Hazrat Noman bin Salim sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye, jabkey hum us waqt masjid key quba mein they. phir sabiqa hadees puri bayan ki."
3987,"Hazrat Noman bin Salim ney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huye suna ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas Banu Saqif key wafad mein hazir huwa. main aap key sath quba mein tha. merey aur aap key ilawa qubey mein mojud sab log so gaey, chunanche itney main eik aadmi aaya aur us ney aap sey koi khufiya baat ki. aap ney farmaya : ja, usey qatl kar dey. phir aap ney puchha : kahin wo ye gawahi to nahin deta ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun? us ney kaha : ye gawahi to wo deta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir rehney dey. phir aap ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo « la Ilaah illa Allah » padh lein. jab wo ye padh lein to unkey jaan o maal qabil ehtiraam ho jatey hain magar ye ke un par Islam ka koi haq banta ho. Muhammad ( ibn Aayun) ney kaha : mainey Shoba sey puchha : kya hadees mein ye alfaz nahin hain : ( أَلَیْسَ یَشْہَدُ أَنْ لَّا إِلٰہَ إِلَّا اللّٰہُ ) ? unhoney farmaya : mera khayal hai ke (ye alfaz ) hain, jabkey main nahin janta."
3988,Hazrat Noman bin Salim sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Amr bin Aus ney bayan kya ke merey walid mohtaram Hazrat Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon sey ladun yahan tak ke wo ye gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin. phir unkey jaan o maal qabil ehtiraam ho jatey hain illa ye ke unkey zimmey Islam ka koi haq banta ho.
3989,"Hazrat abu Idrees bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko khutba irshad farmatey suna, aur wo Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bahut kam riwaayat bayan kartey they, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khutbey mein irshad farmatey suna : ummid hai ke Allah Taala har gunah maaf farma dey magar ye ke koi shakhs kisi momin ko jaan-bujh kar qatl kar dey ya kufr ki haalat mein faut ho jaey."
3990,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo bhi shakhs nahaq maara jata hai uskey qatl ka bojh Hazrat Adam key betey, (Qaabeel) jo sab sey pehla qatil tha, par bhi hoga kyonkey us ney sab sey pehley qatl ko jari kiya tha."
3991,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! albatta momin ka (nahaq) qatl Allah Taala key yahan sari duniya ki tabahi sey ziyada holnaak hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : (is hadees ka eik raawi) Ibrahim bin Muhaajir qawi nahin (zaeef) hai.
3992,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : duniya ka tabah ho jana Allah Taala key nazdik eik musalman shakhs key (nahaq) qatl key muqabley mein bahut maamuli hai.
3993,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik momin ka qatl Allah Taala key nazdik puri duniya ki tabahi sey ziyada bada hai.
3994,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik momin ka qatl Allah Taala key nazdik duniya ki tabahi sey ziyada ahmiyat rakhta hai.
3995,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin ka qatl Allah Taala key nazdik puri duniya ki tabahi sey badh kar hai.
3996,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aadmi sey sab sey pehley jis chiz ka hisab liya jaeyga, wo namaz hai. aur logon key darmiyan sab sey pehley faisla qatl key barey mein hoga."
3997,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sab sey pehley logon mein qatl waghera key faisley kiye jaeyngey.
3998,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke qiyamat key din logon key darmiyan sab sey pehley qatl key faisley kiye jaeyngey.
3999,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke qiyamat key din logon key darmiyan sab sey pehley qatl waghera key faisley hongey.
4000,Hazrat Amr bin Shurehbil (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din sab sey pehley logon key darmiyan qatl waghera key faisley kiye jaeyngey.
4001,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke sab sey pehley logon key darmiyan qatl key faisley hongey.
4002,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qiyamat key din) eik aadmi dusrey aadmi ka haath pakdey huye aayega aur duhaai dega : aey merey Rab ! us ney mujhey qatl kya tha. Allah Taala qatil sey farmaeyga : tu ney is ko kyon qatl kiya tha? wo kahega : ya Allah ! mainey is liye qatl kiya taake terey Deen ko ghalba hasil ho. Allah Taala farmaeyga : ye to mera haq hai. eik aur aadmi eik dusrey aadmi ka haath pakdey huye aayega aur kahega : Maula ! us ney mujhey qatl kiya tha. Allah Taala farmaeyga : tu ney isey kyon qatl kiya tha? wo kahega : is liye ke falan ki izzat aur ghalba qaaim rahey. Allah Taala farmaeyga : izzat to usey nahin mil sakti, phir wo qatil apney gunah samet loteyga (apney kiye ki saza paeyga)."
4003,Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey falan shakhs ney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din maqtool apney qatil ko ley kar (Allah taala key huzur) pesh hoga aur kahega : is sey poochh ke us ney mujhey kyon qatl kiya tha? wo kahega : mainey isey falan ki hukumat ki khatir qatl kiya tha. Hazrat Jundub ney farmaya : aisey kaam sey bacho.
4004,"Hazrat Salim bin Abul-Ja'ad sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey us shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo kisi momin ko jaan boojhkar (nahaq) qatl kar dey, phir tauba karey aur eman ley aaye aur nek kaam karney lagey aur raahe-raast par aa jaey. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : uskey liye tauba ki gunjaaish kaisey ho sakti hai ke mainey tumharey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : maqtool apney qatil ko pakad kar laayega. uski ragon sey khoon beh raha hoga. wo kahega : aey merey Rab ! is sey poochh is ney mujhey kis jurm mein qatl kiya? phir Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! yaqinan ye aayat Allah Taala hi ney utaari hai magar phir usey mansookh nahin farmaya."
4005,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey marwi hai ke ehle-Kufa ka aayat : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan-boojh kar qatl karey … .'' mein ikhtilaf ho gaya, to main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur un sey puchha to unhoney farmaya : ye aayat aakhiri daur mein nazil hui hai, phir isey kisi aur aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya."
4006,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya us shakhs ki tauba qubul ho sakti hai jisney kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar diya ho? unhoney farmaya : nahin. mainey unhein Sura furqan wali aayat padh kar sunai : (و الذین لا یدعون مع اللہ الہا اخر و لا یقتلون النفس التی حرم اللہ الا بالحق),''woh log jo Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey aur kisi shakhs ko nahaq qatl nahin kartey jisey Allah ney haram kiya hai magar haq key sath.''unhoney farmaya : ye Makki aayat hai. Is ko dusri madni aayat ney mansookh kar diya : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاء ہ جہنم), ''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey, uski saza jahannam hai … الخ.''"
4007,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Laila ney farmaya ke main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey in do aayaton key barey mein poochhun. eik to ye aayat hai : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاء ہ جہنم),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko qasdan qatl kar dey, uski saza jahannam hai.'' mainey puchha to aap ney farmaya : is aayat ko kisi aur aayat ney mansookh nahin kiya aur dusri aayat hai : (و الذین لا یدعون مع اللہ الہا اخر و لا یقتلون النفس التی حرم اللہ الا بالحق),''jo log Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey aur kisi ko nahaq qatl nahin kartey jisey Allah ney haram kiya hai magar haq key sath.'' farmaya : ye kuffar key barey mein hai."
4008,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke (daure-jahiliyat mein) baaz logon ney qatl kiye they aur bahut ziyada kiye they, zina kiye they aur bahut ziyada kiye they aur hurmaton ko paamaal kiya tha. wo log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! jo baat aap kartey hain aur jiski aap dawat detey hain, bahut achchhi hai ba-sharte-ke aap hamein ye bataeyn ke hamarey guzishta aamal ka kaffara mumkin hai? to Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaar di : (و الذین لا یدعون مع اللہ الہا اخر … الخ),''jo log Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey … Allah Taala un ki buraiyon ko nekiyon mein badal dega.''yani Allah Taala unkey shirk ko eman aur unkey zina ko pak damani sey badal dega. aur ye aayat bhi utri : (قل یعبادی الذین اسرفوا Ali (Raziallahu anhu) انفسھم),''keh dijiye : aey merey bando ! jinhoney apney aap par ziyadti ki hai … الخ ۔.''"
4009,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mushrik log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : jo baat aap farmatey hain aur jis baat ki aap dawat detey hain, wo bahut achchhi hai ba-sharte-ke aap hamein bataeyn ke hamarey guzishta aamal ka kaffara mumkin hai? to ye aayat utri : (و الذین لا یدعون مع اللہ الہا اخر),''aur jo log Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey … الخ.'' aur ye aayat utri : (قل یعبادی الذین اسرفوا Ali (Raziallahu anhu) انفسھم), ''keh dijiye : aey merey bando ! jinhoney apney aap par ziyadti ki hai (yani gunah kiye hain) … الخ.''"
4010,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke qiyamat key din maqtool apney qatil ko sar key agley baalon sey pakad kar layega jabkey uski gardan ki ragon sey khoon beh raha hoga. wo kahega : aey merey Rab ! is ney mujhey qatl kya tha yahan tak ke wo usey arsh sey qarib kar dega. logon ney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey uski tauba ka zikr kiya to unhoney ye aayat tilawat farmaee : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاء ہ جہنم خلدا فیھا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey … الخ.'' aur farmaya : jab sey ye aayat utri hai, mansookh nahin hui. uskey liye tauba kaisey mumkin hai?"
4011,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ye aayat : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاء ہ جہنم خلدا فیھا),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kerey. uski saza jahannam hai. is mein hamesha rahega … الخ.'' soora furqan wali aayat sey chhe maah baad utri hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Muhammad bin Amr ney ye riwayat abu Zinaad sey nahin suni (is tarah ye sanad munqata' ho gaee)."
4012,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke ye aayat : (و من یقتل مؤمنا متعمدا فجزاء ہ جہنم),''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar (nahaq) qatl kar dey, uski saza jahannam hai … الخ.'' Soora furqan wali (aainda) aayat sey aath maah baad nazil hui hai : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ مَعَ اللّٰہِ اِلٰہًا آخَرَ وَلَا یَقْتُلُوْنَ النَّفْسَ الَّتِیْ حَرَّمَ اللّٰہُ اِلَّا بِالْحَقِّ),''jo log Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey aur kisi jaan ko nahaq qatl nahin kartey jisey Allah ney haram kiya hai. magar haq key sath … الخ.'' Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke (agli riwayat mein) Abu-Zinad ney apney aur Khaarija key darmiyan (taud khatam karney key liye) Mujaalid bin Auf dakhil kar diya hai."
4013,"Hazrat Khaarija bin Zaid bin Sabit apney walid mohtaram (Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu)) sey bayan farmatey hain ke jab ye aayat utri : (وَ مَنْ یَّقْتُلْ مُؤْمِنًا مُّتَعَمِّدًا فَجَزَآؤُہٗ جَہَنَّمُ خٰلِدًا فِیْہَا), ''jo shakhs kisi momin ko jaan boojh kar qatl kar dey to uski saza jahannam hai, wo is mein hamesha rahega.'' to hum bahut darey. phir wo aayat utri jo Sura furqan mein hai : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ مَعَ اللّٰہِ اِلٰہًا آخَرَ وَلَا یَقْتُلُوْنَ النَّفْسَ الَّتِیْ حَرَّمَ اللّٰہُ اِلَّا بِالْحَقِّ),''jo log Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey aur na kisi jaan ko nahaq qatl kartey hain jisey Allah ney haram kiya hai. magar haq key sath … الخ.''"
4014,"Hazrat Abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo Allah Taala key paas is haal mein hazir huwa ke wo Allah Taala ki ibadat karta raha ho aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na banaya ho, namaz pabandi key sath padhta raha ho, Zakat (puri ki puri) deta raha ho aur kabeera gunahon sey bacha raha ho, uskey liye jannat hai. logon ney aap sey kabeera gunahon key barey mein puchha (ke wo kon kon sey hain?) to aap ney (bator misal) irshad farmaya : Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek banana, musalman shakhs ko qatl karna aur ladaai key din bhag jana."
4015,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey gunah ye hain : Allah Taala key sath shirk karna, waliden ki nafarmani karna, kisi shakhs ko nahaq qatl karna aur jhooti gawahi dena."
4016,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : badey gunah : Allah Taala key sath shareek thehrana, waliden ki nafarmani karna, nahaq qatl karna aur jhooti qism khana hain."
4017,"Hazrat Ubaid bin umr sey riwayat hai ke mujhey merey walid mohtaram ney bayan farmaya, aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahabi they, ke eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! badey badey gunah kon sey hain? aap ney farmaya : wo saat hain. un mein sey sab sey bada Allah Taala key sath shareek thehrana hai. (deegar ye hain : ) kisi shakhs ko nahaq qatl karna aur jang key din maidan sey bhag jana waghera. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
4018,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! kon sa gunah sab sey bada hai? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala ka shareek banaey, halanke us ney tujhey paida kya hai. mainey kaha : phir kon sa? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to apney bachey ko is liye qatl kar dey ke wo terey sath khaeyga. mainey arz kya : phir kon sa? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to apney padosi ki biwi sey zina kerey."
4019,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa gunah sab sey bada hai? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala ka shareek banaey , halanke us ney tujhey paida kiya hai. mainey kaha : phir kon sa ? aap ney farmaya : ( phir ) ye ke to apney bachchey ko is bina par qatl kar dey ke wo terey sath khayega. mainey arz kiya : phir kon sa? farmaya : (phir) ye ke to apney padoshi ki biwi sey zina kerey."
4020,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha : sab sey bada gunah kon sa hai? aap ney farmaya : shirk , ke to Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek banaey. aur ye ke to apney padoshi ki biwi sey bad-kari kerey. aur ye ke to apney bachchey ko faqr (gharibi) key dar sey maar dey ke wo terey sath khayega. phir Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney ye aayat padhi : (وَالَّذِیْنَ لَا یَدْعُوْنَ مَعَ اللّٰہِ اِلٰہًا آخَرَ),''(Allah key bandey wo hain) jo Allah Taala key sath kisi dusrey mabood ko nahin pukartey … الخ ۔.''Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat (Aasim an abi Waeyl) ghalat hai jabkey sahih riwayat is sey pehli (واصل عن ابی وائل) hai. Yazid ki ye riwayat (jis mein us ney Wasil ki bajaey Aasim kaha hai) ghalat hai. asal mein (Aasim nahin balke) Wasil hai."
4021,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key siwa koi mabood nahin ! kisi musalman aadmi ka, jo gawahi deta ho ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah Taala ka Rasool hun, khoon bahana jayez nahin, siwaye teen aadmiyon key : (eik ) wo jo Islam chhod kar kafir ban jaey aur musalmanon ki jamaat chhod jaey, aur (doosra) wo jo shaadi shuda ho kar zina kerey. aur (teesra) wo jo kisi jaan ko nahaq qatl kerey. Aa'mash ney kaha : mainey ye riwayat Ibrahim Nakhai sey bayan ki to unhoney mujhey (اسود عن عائشۃ) (ki sanad) sey is jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
4022,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke kya tujhey malum nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman shakhs ka khoon bahana jayez nahin magar (teen aadmiyon ka : ) wo aadmi jisney shaadi shuda honey key baad zina kiya aur wo shakhs jisney Islam laney key baad kufr kiya ya qatil ko qisaas mein maara jaeyga. is riwayat ko zuhair ney maqoof bayan kiya hai.
4023,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke aey Ammaar ! kya to nahin janta ke teen ashkhaas key ilawa kisi musalman ka khoon bahana halal nahin : jaan key badley jaan, ya (us aadmi ko rajam (sangsar) kiya jaeyga) jisney shaadi shuda honey key baad zina kiya. phir raawi ney puri hadees bayan ki."
4024,"Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sahal (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat Abdullah bin Aamir bin Rabeea (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke jab Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ghirey huey they to hum unkey paas bethey they. jab hum (kisi jagah sey) wahan jatey to balaat walon ki baaten suntey they. eik din Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi us jagah gaey, phir hamari taraf nikley aur farmaya : ye log mujhey qatl ki dhamki detey hain. hamney kaha : Allah Taala aap ko un sey kifaayat farmaeyga. aap ney farmaya : aakhir ye mujhey kyon qatl kartey hain? mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : kisi musalman aadmi ka khoon teen (jaraaim) main sey kisi eik key baghair jayez nahin : (eik) wo shakhs jisney Islam laney key baad kufr kiya. (doosra) wo jisney shaadi shuda honey key baad zina kiya. (teesra) wo shakhs jisney kisi ko nahaq qatl kiya. Allah ki qism ! mainey na kufr ki haalat mein zina kiya hai na Islam ki haalat mein. aur jab sey Allah Taala ney mujhey hidayat di hai, mainey kabhi socha tak nahin ke mujhey merey Deen key ilawa koi aur Deen miley. aur mainey kabhi kisi (musalman) ko qatl nahin kiya. to phir wo mujhey kyon qatl kartey hain?"
4025,"Hazrat Arfaja bin Shureh Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko member par logon ko khutba irshad farmatey dekha, aap ney farmaya : merey baad bahut sey fitna aur fasad barpa hongey. jis shakhs ko tum dekho ke wo (musalmanon ki) jamaat sey alag ho gaya hai ya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat mein phoot dalna chahta hai, jo bhi ho usey qatl kar do. bilashuba jamaat par Allah Taala ka haath hota hai. aur shetan us shakhs key sath hota hai jo jamaat sey juda huwa, wo usey laat maar kar haanktaa hai."
4026,"Hazrat Arfaja bin Shureh (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad bahut si kharabiyan aur shar aur fasad hoga … phir aap ney apney haath uthaey … jis shakhs ko tum dekho ke wo ummate Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mein tafriq (farq) paida karna chahta hai jabkey ummat muttafiq aur muttahid hai to usey qatl kar do, chahey wo koi bhi ho."
4027,Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : merey baad bahut si kharabiyan aur fasad hongey. jo shakhs ummatey-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mein phoot dalna chahey jabkey ummat (eik shakhs par) muttafiq ho to usey talwaar sey maar do.
4028,"Hazrat Usama bin shareek (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs meri ummat mein phoot dalney key liye nikley, uski gardan uda do."
4029,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke ukul qabila key aath aadmi Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye (aur qubuley-Islam zahir kiya). phir unhoney Madina ki aab aur huwa ko muwaafiq na paya aur unkey jism kamzor pad gaey. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey is baat ki shikayat ki. aap ney farmaya : tum hamarey charwahey key sath uskey (bahir rehney waley) oonton mein kyon nahin chaley jatey ke tum un oonton key doodh aur peshab piyo? unhoney kaha : theek hai. wo wahan chaley gaey aur (oonton ka) doodh aur peshab peetey rahey. wo tandurust ho gaey to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key charwahey ko qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen pakadney key liye aadmi bhejey. unhoney un logon ko ja pakda, chunanche in ko aap key paas laya gaya to aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye aur un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherin, phir in ko dhoop mein phenk diya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey."
4030,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Ukal qabiley key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye (aur musalman ho gaey). phir unhoney Madina Munawra ki aab aur hawa ko naa-muwaafiq paya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke wo sadqey key oonton mein chaley jaeyn. aur unkey doodh aur peshab piyen. unhoney aisey kiya (tu sehat mand ho gaey). phir unhoney charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur oonton ko haank kar ley gaey. Nabi Mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki talash mein aadmi bhejey. unhen pakad kar laya gaya to aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye. aur un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherin, phir aap ney unkey zakhmon (ko dagh laga kar un) ka khoon band nahin kiya balke in ko (isi tarah) chhod diya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey. phir Allah Taala ney ye aayat utaari : (اِنَّمَا جَزٰٓؤُا الَّذِیْنَ … ),''bilashuba jo log Allah aur uskey Rasool sey jang kartey hain, un ki saza ye hai … الخ.''"
4031,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke ukul qabiley key aath aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. uskey baad raawi ney sabiqa hadees ki tarah hadees bayan ki. aakhir mein hai : aap ney unkey zakhmon ka khoon band na kiya. raawi ney ye bhi kaha ke unhoney charwahey ko qatl kar diya tha.
4032,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Ukul ya Uraina qabiley key kuchh log Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye. Madina Munawra ki aab aur hawa unhen raas na aai to aap ney in ko apney oonton mein janey ka hukm diya ke wo unkey doodh aur peshab piyen. unhoney (sehat-mand honey key baad) charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur oont haank kar ley gaey. aap ney un ki talash mein apney aadmi bhejey, phir aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye aur un ki aankhen (garm salaiyon sey) buri tarah phod den."
4033,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Uraina qabiley key kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye (aur Islam qubul kiya), phir unhoney Madina Munawra ki aab aur huwa ko naa-muwaafiq paya to Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney in ko apney oonton mein bhej diya. unhoney (chand din tak) unka doodh aur peshab piya. jab wo tandurust ho gaey to wo Islam sey murtad ho gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahibe-emaan charwahey ko qatl kiya aur oont haank kar chaltey baney. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki talash mein aadmi bhejey. wo pakad kar laye gaey. aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye. un ki aakhon mein salaiyan pher kar in ko phod diya aur unhen sooli par latka diya."
4034,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Uraina qabiley key kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein farmaya : agar tum hamarey oonton mein ja kar raho aur unka doodh aur peshab piyo (to tumhari sehat key liye behtar hoga). unhoney isi tarah kiya, phir jab wo tandurust ho gaey to uthey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur dobara kafir ban gaey, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key oont haank kar ley gaey. aap ney un ki talash mein aadmi bhejey. unhen laya gaya to aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye aur un ki aankhen phod dein."
4035,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Uraina qabiley key kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye. unhoney Madina ki aab aur hawa ko muwaafiq na paya. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : agar tum hamarey (sehra mein charney waley) oonton mein ja kar raho aur unkey doodh aur peshab piyo (tu tumhari sehat key liye behtar hoga). wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key oonton mein ja kar rehney lagey. jab wo tandurust ho gaey to bawajud Islam qubul karney key kafir ban gaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahibe-emaan charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key oont haank kar chaltey baney. goya un ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey jang ho gaee. aap ney un ki talash mein kuchh aadmi bhejey. unhen pakad kar laya gaya. aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye aur un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherin."
4036,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Uraina qabiley key kuchh log musalman huye, phir unhoney Madina Munawra ki aab aur hawa ko muwaafiq na paya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen farmaya : agar tum hamarey oonton mein ja kar raho aur unka doodh aur peshab piyo (to ye tumhari sehat key liye behtar hoga). unhoney isi tarah kiya. chunanche jab wo tandurust ho gaey to wo Islam sey kufr ki taraf lot gaey, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key musalman charwahey ko qatl kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key oont haank liye aur elaniya bghawat kartey huye bhag khadey huye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey peechhey aadmi bhejey to wo log pakdey gaey, chunanche (unhen pakad kar) aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye, un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pherin aur in ko pathreeley maidan mein chhod diya yahan tak ke wo (eidiyaan ragadte piyasey) mar gaey."
4037,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Ukul ya Uraina qabiley mein sey kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum doodh par guzaaraa karney waley log hain, hum kaasht-kaar nahin. (wajeh ye thi ke) unhen Madina Munawra ki aab aur hawa raas na aai thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke hamarey oonton aur charwahey key paas raho aur oonton ka doodh aur peshab piyo. wo harra key eik kinarey mein rehtey they, phir jab wo tandurust ho gaey to Islam sey murtad ho kar kafir ban gaey. unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur oont haank kar chaltey baney. aap ney unkey peechhey talash karney waley bhejey. unhen pakad laya gaya, chunanche aap ney un ki aankhen (garm salaiyon sey) phod dein. unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye, phir unhein isi haalat mein Harra (garm pathreeley maidan) main chhod diya yahan tak ke wo mar gaey."
4038,Muhammad bin Musanna ney bhi abdul-a'alaa sey usi (mazkura baala riwayat ki ) tarah bayan kya hai.
4039,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke uraina qabiley key kuch log harra key maidan mein utrey, phir wo Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye. unhoney Madina Munawra ki aab o huwa ko muwaafiq na paya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen hukm diya ke wo sadqey key oonton mein rahen aur unkey doodh aur peshab piyen , phir unhoney charwahey ko qatl kya, Islam sey murtad ho gaey aur oont haank kar ley gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey peechey aadmi bhejey. in ko pakad laya gaya to aap ney unkey haath paon sakhti key sath kaat diye, unki aakhon ko phod diya aur unhen garm pathriley maidan mein chhod diya. (Hazrat Anas ney farmaya : ) Allah ki qism ! mainey dekha ke wo piyas ki bina par zamin par daant maar rahey they yahan tak ke isi tarah mar gaey."
4040,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke uraina qabiley key kuch baddu Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur Islam qubul kya, phir unhen Madina ki aab o huwa raas na aai yahan tak ke unkey rang zard pad gaey aur pet badh gaey. to Allah Taala key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney in ko apney oonton mein bhej diya aur unhen unkey doodh aur peshab peeney ka hukm diya yahan tak ke wo tandurust ho gaey. baad Azan unhoney oonton key charwaahon ko qatl kar diya aur oont haank kar ley gaey. Allah Taala key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki talash mein aadmi bhejey. unhen laya gaya to aap ney unkey haath paon kaat diye aur un ki aakhon mein garm salaiyan pher din. jab Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ye hadees bayan farma rahey they to Amirul-momeneen abdul-Malik ney un sey puchha ke unkey sath ye sulook unkey kufr ki wajeh sey kya ya unkey gunah ki wajeh sey ? farmaya : kufr ki wajeh sey."
4041,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke kuch Arab log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur Islam qubul kya, phir wo bimar ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen oonton mein bhej diya taake wo unkey doodh piyen. wo un mein rahey, phir unhoney mansuba bana kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghulam charwahey ko qatl kar diya aur oont haank kar ley gaey. sahaba farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dua farmaai : aey Allah ! us shakhs ko piyasa maar jisney aal Muhammad ko raat piyasa rakh key maara. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un ki talash mein aadmi bhejey. wo pakdey gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sakhti key sath unkey haath paon kaat diye . aur un ki aakhon ko ( garm salaiyon sey) phod diya. baaz ustaad dusron sey ziyada bayan kartey hain, Muawiya ney us hadees mein kaha ke wo oonton ko mushrekin key ilaqey ki taraf haank kar ley gaey."
4042,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke kuch logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki doodh wali oontniyon ko loot liya tha. aap ney in ko giraftar kya, phir sakhti key sath unkey haath paon kaat diye aur un ki aakhon ko phod diya."
4043,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke kuch logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki doodh wali oontniyaan loot lin, chunanche unhen ( pakad kar) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya to Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sakhti key sath unkey haath paon kaat diye aur un ki aakhon ko ( garm salaiyon sey) phod diya. ye alfaz ibn musannaa key hain."
4044,Hazrat Hisham key walid (Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber ) sey riwayat hai ke kuch logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key oont lot liye they. aap ney sakhti key sath unkey haath paon kaat diye aur un ki aankhen phod din.
4045,"Hazrat Urwa bin Zuber sey marwi hai ke Uraina qabiley key kuch logon ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki doodh wali oontniyan loot lin aur unhen haank ley gaey. aur aap key eik ghulam (charwahey) ko bhi qatl kar diya. aap ney unkey peechey aadmi dorraye, chunanche wo ( qatil ) pakad liye gaey. aap ney unkey haath paon kaat diye aur aankhen phod den."
4046,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney bhi ye riwayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey naqal farmaai hai. is mein ye lafz bhi hain ke unkey barey mein muhaarba wali aayat utri.
4047,Hazrat Abu-Zinad sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney un logon key haath kaatey jinhoney aap ki doodh wali oontniyaan churaai thin aur un ki aankhen aag (par garm ki hui salaiyon) key sath phod din to Allah Taala ney is barey mein aap par izhare-narazi farmaya aur ye puri aayat utri : { اِنَّمَا جَزٰٓؤُا الَّذِیْنَ یُحَارِبُوْنَ اللّٰہَ وَ رَسُوْلَہٗ }
4048,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unki aankhen is liye phodi thin ke unhoney charwaahon ki aankhen phodi thin.
4049,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi aadmi ney ansaar ki eik ladki ko uskey zewrat lootney key liye qatl kar diya aur uska sar pathar sey kuchal kar usey eik puraney kunwen mein phenk diya. us Yahudi ko pakad kar laya gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke usey pathar sey kuchla jaey yahan tak ke wo mar jaey.
4050,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney ansaar ki eik ladki ko uskey zewrat ki khatir qatl kar diya, phir usey puraney kunwen mein phenk diya. (darasal) us ney us ka sar pathar sey kuchal diya tha. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke usey pathar key sath kuchla jaey yahan tak ke wo mar jaey."
4051,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke aayat mubaraka : « { اِنَّمَا جَزٰٓؤُا الَّذِیْنَ یُحَارِبُوْنَ اللّٰہَ وَ رَسُوْلَہٗ … الخ } » mushrekin key barey mein utri hai. un mein sey agar koi shakhs pakdey janey sey pehley pehley tauba kar ley to is par saza nafiz karney ki ijazat nahin, lekin ye aayat musalman shakhs key liye nahin hai, lihaza agar koi musalman kisi ko qatl kar dey ya zamin mein fasad karey (daka daley ya baghawat kerey) ya Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey jang karey (murtad ho jaey) phir wo kafiron sey ja miley aur usey pakda na ja sakey to ye chiz is par mutalliqa had qaaim karney sey rukawat na hogi."
4052,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney khutbey mein sadqa karney ki targheeb dilaaya kartey they aur Musla karney sey mana farmaya kartey they.
4053,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman shakhs ka khoon bahana jayez nahin magar teen jaraaim mein sey kisi eik jurm ki bina par : shaadi-shuda zaani ko rajm kya jaeyga. ya jo shakhs kisi dusrey shakhs ko jaan-bujh kar qatl kar dey, usey qisas mein qatl kya jaeyga. ya jo shakhs Islam sey murtad ho jaey aur Allah azz-w-jall aur uskey Rasool sey jang karey usey bhi qatl kya jaeyga ya sooli par latkaayaa jaeyga ya usey jala watan kya jaeyga."
4054,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ghulam bula ijazat bhag jaey to uski namaz qubul nahin hoti yahan tak ke wo apney malikon key paas wapis lot aaye.
4055,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan farmatey hain ke (aap ney farmaya :) jab koi ghulam apney Malik sey bhag jaey to uski namaz qubul nahin hoti. agar wo mar jaey to kufr ki haalat mein mareyga. Hazrat Jareer ka eik ghulam bhag gaya tha. wo un ki giraft mein aaya to unhoney uski gardan utaar di.
4056,Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab koi ghulam bhag kar mushrekin (aur kuffar) key ilaqey mein chala jaey to uskey liye musalmanon ki aman aur panah nahin rehti ( yani usey qatl kya ja sakta hai ).
4057,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab ghulam bhag kar mushrekin key ilaqey mein chala jaey to us ka khoon bahana jayez ho jata hai.
4058,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi ghulam bhag kar kuffar key ilaqey mein chala jaey to us ka khoon bahana halal ho jata hai.
4059,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jo ghulam bhag kar kafiron key ilaqey mein chala jaey. uska khoon halal ho jata hai.
4060,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jo ghulam bhag kar mushrikon key ilaqey mein chala jaey, us ka khoon bahana jayez ho jata hai."
4061,"Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jo ghulam apney malikon sey bhag kar Islam key dushman sey ja miley, us ney apna khoon ( musalmanon key liye) halal kar diya."
4062,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : kisi musalman shakhs ka khoon bahana jayez nahin magar teen jaraaim mein sey kisi eik ki bina par : jo shakhs shaadi shuda honey key baad zina kerey. is par rajm ki saza hai. jo shakhs kisi ko jaan-bujh kar nahaq qatl kar dey to usey qisas mein qatl kar diya jaeyga aur jo shakhs Islam laney key baad murtad ho jaey to usey bhi qatl kar diya jaeyga.
4063,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : teen jaraaim key baghair kisi musalman ka khoon bahana jayez nahin : wo shaadi shuda honey key baad zina karey ya kisi insan ko qatl karey to usey qatl kya jaeyga. ya musalman honey key baad kafir bin jaey to usey bhi qatl kya jaeyga.
4064,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apna Deen badley ( Islam ko chhod kar koi doosra Deen ikhtiyar kar ley) usey qatl kar do.
4065,"Hazrat ikrima sey riwayat hai ke kuch log Islam sey murtad ho gaey. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen aag mein jala diya. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya agar main saza deta to main unhen aag mein na jilata kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : tum kisi ko Allah wala azab na do. agar main unhen saza deta to unhen sirf qatl hi kar deta kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya hai : jo shakhs apna Deen badal ley, usey qatl kar do."
4066,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman apna Deen badal ley, usey qatl kar do."
4067,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman apna Deen badal ley, usey qatl kar do."
4068,"Hazrat Hasan Basri sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (musalman honey key baad) apna Deen badal ley, usey qatl kar do. Imam abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees ibaad ki hadees sey ziyada durust hai."
4069,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman apna Deen badal ley, usey qatl kar do."
4070,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key paas kuch Sudani (ya Hindustani) log laye gaey jinhoney ( Islam laney key baad ) eik but ki puja shuru kar di thi. aap ney unhen aag mein jala diya. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney to farmaya tha : jo musalman apna Deen badal ley usey qatl kar do.
4071,"Hazrat abu-Barda apney walid mohtaram (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey bayan farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen Yamen ki taraf (haakim bana kar) bheja. phir uskey baad Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja. jab wo aaye to kehney lagey : aey logo! main tumhari taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka qaasid hun. Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey liye takiya ya gadda rakha taake wo is par bethein. itney main eik aadmi laya gaya jo pehley Yahudi tha, phir musalman ho gaya, phir kafir ban gaya. Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main nahin bethunga yahan tak ke usey qatl kar diya jaey. ye Allah Taala aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla hai. teen martaba farmaya, phir jab usey qatl kar diya gaya to aap bethey."
4072,"Hazrat Musab bin Saad apney walid mohtaram (Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey bayan farmatey hain : jis din Makka Mukarrama fatah huwa , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar mardon aur do aurton key siwa tamam logon ko aman dey di. aap ney farmaya : agar tum in ko Kaba sharif key pardon sey latka huwa pao , tab bhi qatl kar do. ( wo chaar mard ye they : ) ikrima bin abi jahal, Abdullah bin khatal, maqees bin Sababa aur Abdullah bin Saad bin abi Sarah. Abdullah bin khatal Kabey key pardon sey latka huwa paya gaya. Hazrat Saeed bin Hures aur Hazrat Ammaar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) uski taraf lapkey. Saeed Ammaar sey pehley pahunch gaey kyonkey wo Ammaar ki nisbat jawan they. unhoney usey qatl kar diya. Maqis bin Sababa ko logon ney bazar mein pakad liya aur qatl kar diya. ikrima bhag kar samandar mein kashti par sawar ho gaya. bahut tez hawa chal padi. (kashti toofan mein phans gaee.) kashti waley kehney lagey : ab khalis Allah Taala ko pukaro kyonkey tumharey mabood ( but waghera ) yahan ( toofan mein) tumhen koi faeyda nahin dey saktey. ikrima ney kaha : agar samandar mein khalis Allah Taala ko pukarney key ilawa najat nahin to khushki mein bhi khalis Allah Taala ko pukarey baghair najat nahin mil sakti. aey Allah ! main tujh sey ehad karta hun ke agar to mujhey is musibat sey, jismein main phans chuka hun, bacha ley to main zarur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas ja kar apna haath unkey haath mein dey dunga aur mujhey yaqin hai ke main unhen bahut ziyada maaf karney wala aur ehsan karney wala paonga. phir wo aaye aur musalman ho gaey. baqi raha Abdullah bin abi Sarah! to wo Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) key paas chup gaya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko baiat key liye bulaya to Hazrat Usman usey ley kar aaye yahan tak ke usey bilkul aap key paas khada kar diya aur arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! Abdullah sey baiat ley lein. aap sar utha kar usey dekhney lagey. teen baar Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ney yehi guzarish ki. aap har dafa ( amalan ) inkar farma rahey they. aakhir teesri baar key baad aap ney baiat le li, phir aap apney sahaba ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : kya tum mein koi samajh daar shakhs nahin tha ke jab tum dekh rahey they ke mainey uski baiat leney sey haath rok rakha hai to koi shakhs uthta aur usey qatl kar deta. unhoney arz ki : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamen malum na tha ke aap key dil mein kya hai? aap aankh sey halka sa ishara farma detey. aap ney farmaya : Nabi key laaiq nahin ke uski aankh khaain ho."
4073,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Ansaar mein sey eik aadmi musalman ho gaya, phir murtad ho gaya aur mushrikon sey ja mila. baad iske wo sharminda huwa to usney apni qom ko pegham bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey poochho, kya meri tauba qubul ho sakti hai? uski qom key log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur kehney lagey ke falan shakhs naadim hai aur us ney hamein pegham diya hai ke hum aap sey poochhen, kya uski tauba qubul ho sakti hai? chunanche ye aayat utri : (کَیْفَ یَہْدِی اللّٰہُ قَوْمًا کَفَرُوْا بَعْدَ اِیْمَانِہِمْ … غَفُوْرٌ رَّحِیْمٌ),''Allah taala un logon ko kaisey hidayat dega jo apney eman laney key baad kafir ho gaey, jabkey wo gawahi dey chukey ke be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bar-haq hain aur unkey paas wazeh nishaniyan aa chukin aur Allah zalim qom ko hidayat nahin deta. un logon ki saza yehi hai ke un par Allah ki, farishton ki aur sab logon ki lanat hai. wo us (lanat) main hamesha rahen gey, un sey azab na to halka kiya jaeyga aur na in ko mohlat hi di jaeygi. magar jin logon ney iskey baad tauba kar key apni islah kar li, be-shak Allah Taala bahut darguzar aur nihayat reham karney wala hai.''phir usey pegham bheja gaya aur wo musalman ho gaya."
4074,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney Sura Nahal ki aayat : (مَنْ کَفَرَ بِاللّٰہِ مِنْ بَعْدِ اِیْمَانِہٖٓ اِلَّا مَنْ اُکْرِہَ … ),''jo shakhs apney eman laney key baad kufr karey. siwaye iskey jis par jabr kiya gaya aur us ka dil eman par mutmain tha, lekin jisney kufr key liye apna Sina khol diya (razi khushi kufr kiya) to aisey logon par Allah ka ghazab hai aur unkey liye bahut bada azab hai.'' key barey mein farmaya ke phir isey mansookh kar diya gaya, yani is sey ye mustashnaa kar liya gaya. (ثُمَّ اِنَّ رَبَّکَ لِلَّذِیْنَ ہَاجَرُوْا … ),""phir tera Rab un logon ko jinhoney aazmaaish mein padney key baad hijrat ki, phir jihad kiya aur sabr kiya (sabit qadam rahey) beshak aap ka Rab un (aazmaeshon) key baad (un logon ko) bahut maaf farmanewala aur reham karney wala hai.'' is sey murad Abdullah bin Saad bin Abu Sarah hain jo (baad mein Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key daure-Khilaafat mein) Misr key governer rahey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key liye (''wahi'' aur khutoot waghera) likha kartey they. shetan ney unhen phislaa diya aur wo kafiron sey ja miley. fateh Makka key din aap ney unkey qatl ka hukm jari farma diya lekin Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ney unkey liye panah maangi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen panah dey di (aur unka Islam qubul kar liya)."
4075,"Hazrat Usman Shihaam sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke main eik na-bina shakhs ko liye ja raha tha ke main Hazrat Ikrima key paas pahuncha to wo bayan farmaney lagey ke mujhey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney main eik na-bina shakhs tha. uski eik londi thi jis sey uskey do betey bhi they lekin wo aksar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki aeb-juee kiya karti aur aap ko gaaliyaan bakti thi. wo (na-bina shakhs) usey daant'ta tha magar wo baaz na aati thi, wo usey rokta tha magar wo rukti na thi (woh na-bina shakhs kehtey hain : ) eik raat mainey Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr kiya to us ney aap ko phir bura bhala kehna shuru kar diya to main sabr na kar saka. mainey eik khanjar pakda aur uskey pet par rakh kar ooper sey pura bojh dal diya aur usey qatl kar diya. subah hui to uskey qatl ka shor mach gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bhi us (key qatl ) ka tazkira kiya gaya, chunanche aap ney sab logon ko ikhatta kiya aur farmaya : main us shakhs ko jis par mera haq hai aur us ney ye kaam kiya hai, Allah ki qism dey kar kehta hun ke wo khada ho jaey. chunanche wo na-bina shakhs ladkhadaata huwa aaya aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mainey isey qatl kiya hai. ye meri londi thi aur merey sath bahut shafqat aur mohabbat karney wali thi aur is sey merey motiyon jaisey do betey bhi hain lekin wo aksar aap ki aeb-juee kiya karti thi aur aap ko gaaliyaan bikti thi. main usey rokta tha, wo rukti na thi. main usey daantta tha, wo samajhti na thi. guzishta raat mainey aap ka zikr kiya to wo aap ko bura bhala kehney lagi (main sabr na kar saka). mainey khanjar pakda aur uskey pet par rakh kar pura bojh dal diya yahan tak ke mainey usey qatl kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : khabrdar ! gawah raho ke us ka khoon zaya hai (us key qatl ka qisaas hai na diyat)."
4076,Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) key barey mein koi bakwaas bakaa. mainey kaha : main isey qatl kar dun? unhoney mujhey daantaa aur farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad ye kisi ka haq nahin.
4077,Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) eik aadmi par naraz huye (kyonkey us ney aap ko gaali di thi). mainey kaha : aey khalifae-Rasool ! ye kon shakhs hai? farmaya : kyon ? mainey kaha : taake main iski gardan utaar sakun ba-sharte-ke aap mujhey hukm dein. unhoney farmaya : to aisa kar guzreyga? mainey kaha : haan. Hazrat Abu-Barza kehtey hain : Allah ki qism ! jo baat mainey kahi thi uski azmat ney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka ghussa khatam kar diya. phir unhoney farmaya : ye haq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi aur ko hasil nahin.
4078,Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas sey guzra to wo apney sathiyon mein sey kisi aadmi par ghussey ho rahey they. mainey arz kiya : aey khalifae-Rasulullah ! ye kon shakhs hai jis par aap is qadr naraz ho rahey hain? farmaney lagey : tum is barey mein kyon poochh rahey ho? mainey kaha : main iski gardan uda dunga. Hazrat Abu-Barza ney kaha : Allah ki qism ! meri is baat ney unka ghussa khatam kar diya. phir aap ney farmaya : ye Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad (aap key ilawa) kisi ka haq nahin.
4079,Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) kisi aadmi par bahut naraz huye. mainey kaha : agar aap mujhey hukm den to main kar guzrun (isey qatl kar dun). unhoney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi insan ko ye haq hasil nahin.
4080,"Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) eik aadmi par bahut ziyada naraz huye yahan tak ke unka rang badal gaya. mainey arz ki : aey khalifae-Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! agar aap mujhey hukm den to main iski gardan utaar dunga. (meri is baat sey) goya un par thanda pani dal diya gaya, chunanche us shakhs par sey unka ghussa khatam ho gaya. aur farmaney lagey : aey Abu-Barza ! teri maa tujhey gum paey ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi ka ye martaba aur haq nahin. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman Nasai ((Rahmatullahi Alaih)) bayan kartey hain ke ye ghalat hai. durust Abu Nasr hai aur is (Abu Nasr) ka naam Humed bin Hilal hai. Shoba ney Zaid bin Abu Aneesa ki mukhalifat ki hai (yani Amr bin Murra sey uski riwayat mein mukhalifat ki hai)."
4081,"Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya to aap kisi shakhs par sakht naraz ho rahey they. us ney jawaaban aap ko kuchh kaha (badtamizi ki). mainey kaha : main iski gardan na utaar dun? aap ney mujhey daantaa aur farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi ko ye haq hasil nahin. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain ke Abu Nasr ka naam Humaid bin Hilal hai, aur us sey ye hadees Yunus bin Ubaid ney bayan ki to usney us ko musnad, yani muttasil bayan kiya hai."
4082,"Hazrat Abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke hum Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bethey they. aap kisi musalman aadmi par naraz huye aur intehai ziyada naraz huye. jab mainey ye soorate-haal dekhi to mainey kaha : aey khalifae-Rasool ! main iski gardan utaar dun? jab mainey qatl ka zikr kiya to us baat ko aap ney mukammal taur par chhod diya aur idhar-udhar ki baaten shuru kar dein. jab hum mutafarriq (alag-alag) ho gaey to aap ney mujhey pegham bheja aur farmaya : Abu-Barza ! tum ney kya kaha tha? main us waqt tak bhool chuka tha ke mainey kya kaha tha. mainey aap sey kaha : mujhey yad dila dijiye. aap ney farmaya : kya tujhey yad nahin, tu ney kya kaha tha? mainey kaha : Allah ki qism ! nahin. aap ney farmaya : jab tu ney mujhey eik aadmi par naraz hotey dekha to tu ney kaha tha : aey khalifae-Rasool ! main iski gardan utaar dun? kya tujhey ye baat yad nahin? kya to (waqaee) aisa kar deta (yani usey qatl kar deta?) mainey kaha : Allah ki qism ! haan. ab bhi agar aap hukm dein to main ye kaam kar guzrunga. aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! ye rutba Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key baad kisi ka bhi nahin. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke in ahaadees mein ye hadees sab sey behtar aur ahsan hai."
4083,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik Yahudi ney apney sathi sey kaha : aao us Nabi key paas chalen. uskey sathi ney us sey kaha : usey Nabi na kaho. agar us ney teri baat sun li to uski aankhen chaar ho jaeyngi. phir wo dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur aap sey nau wazeh aayaat key barey mein puchha. aap ney un sey farmaya : Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek na banao. chori na karo. zina na karo. kisi qabile-ehtiraam jaan ko nahaq qatl na karo. kisi be-gunah shakhs ko (nahaq saza dilwaney key liye) sahibe-iqtidar key paas na ley jao. jadu na karo. sood na khao. kisi pak daman par ilzam na lagaao jang key din maidane-jang sey na bhago. aur aey yahudiyo ! khas tumharey liye ye hukm hai ke tum haftey key din (ki tazeem) key barey mein (Allah taala key hukm sey) tajawuz na karo (had se aagey na badho). chunanche un dono ney (ye sun kar) aap key haath aur paon chumey aur kaha : hum gawahi detey hain ke yaqinan aap Nabi hain. aap ney farmaya : phir tumhen mera muttabey ban'ney sey kon si chiz maanea' (rukawat) hai? unhoney kaha : Hazrat Dawud (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dua farmaee thi ke hamesha Nabi un ki nasal sey aaye, isi ke sath hum dartey hain ke agar hamney aap ki perwi ki to Yahudi hamein qatl kar dengey."
4084,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney gireh baandhi aur is mein (padh kar) phunka, us ney jadu kiya. aur jisney jadu kiya, us ney shirk kiya aur jis shakhs ney koi (shirkiya) chiz galey mein latkaai, usey isi key supurd kiya jaeyga."
4085,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke eik Yahudi shakhs ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par jadu kar diya. aap uski wajeh sey kuchh din bimar sey rahey. phir Hazrat Jibril alehissalam aap key paas aaye aur farmaya : eik Yahudi ney aap par jadu kar diya hai. us ney kuchh girhein dey kar falan kunwen mein rakh chhodi hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh sahaba bhejey. unhoney un girahon ko nikala aur in ko aap key paas laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) is tarah uth khadey huye jaisey kisi oont ka ghutna khol diya jaey. phir na to aap ney us Yahudi sey us ka zikr kiya aur na us (yahudi) ney kabhi aap key chehrey par us ka kuchh asar paya.
4086,Hazrat Qaabus key walid mohtaram Hazrat Makhaariq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : eik shakhs merey paas aata hai aur mera maal chheen'naa chahta hai. (to main kya karun?) aap ney farmaya : usey Allah Taala ki nasihat kar (uskey azaab sey dara). us ney kaha : agar wo nasihat na maaney to? aap ney farmaya : apney Aas paas key musalmanon sey madad hasil kar. us ney kaha : agar merey Aas paas koi musalman na hon to? aap ney farmaya : Haakim sey madad talab kar. us ney kaha : agar Haakim bhi mujh sey door ho? farmaya : phir apney maal ki hifazat key liye ladaai kar yahan tak ke to (maara jaey aur) aakhirat mein shaheed ban jaey ya apney maal ko bacha ley.
4087,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! farmaiye agar merey maal par hamla kar diya jaey (to kya karun?) aap ney farmaya : unhein Allah Taala ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo na maanen to? farmaya : phir Allah ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo phir bhi na maanen to? farmaya : phir Allah Taala ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo phir bhi Misr rahen to? aap ney farmaya : phir un sey lad. agar to maara gaya to jannat mein jaeyga aur agar tu ney unhen maar diya to wo aag mein jaeyngey.
4088,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat Aaliya mein hazir huwa aur kaha : Allah key Rasool ! farmaiye agar merey maal par hamla kar diya jaey to? aap ney farmaya : in ko Allah ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo (daaku) na maanen? aap ney farmaya : phir Allah ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo phir bhi na maanen to? aap ney farmaya : to phir Allah Taala ka wasta dey. us ney kaha : agar wo phir bhi na maanen to? aap ney farmaya : phir un sey lad. agar to qatl ho gaya to jannat mein jaeyga aur agar tu ney in ko maar diya to wo jahannami hongey.
4089,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo apney maal ko (daakuon waghera sey) bachaney key liye ladaai karey aur maara jaey to wo shaheed hai.
4090,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat mein ladtaa huwa maara jaey, wo shaheed hai."
4091,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo apney maal ki hifazat mein mazloom maara jaey, uskey liye jannat hai."
4092,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat karta huwa maara jaey, wo shaheed hai."
4093,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan farmatey hain ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ka maal nahaq chheenney ki koshish ki jaey aur wo ladtaa huwa maara jaey to wo shaheed hoga. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney farmaya : ) ye (riwayat) ghalat hai. Suaer bin Khums ki (is sey pehli) riwayat durust hai.
4094,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat karta huwa maara jaey, wo shaheed hai."
4095,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat karta huwa maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. ye (hadees) mukhtasar hai."
4096,Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo aadmi apney maal ki hifazat karta huwa ladaai ladey (aur maara jaey) wo shaheed hai.
4097,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ko (daakuon sey) bachatey huye maara jaey, wo shaheed hai."
4098,"Hazrat Abu-Jafar sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi zalim key muqabley mein maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Muammal ki (sabiqa (pichhli)) hadees ghalat hai jabkey Abdur-Rehman ki (yehi) hadees durust hai."
4099,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo apney maal ki hifazat kartey huye maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. aur jo apni jaan bachatey huye maara jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai aur jo shakhs apney ghar walon key difaa mein maara jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai."
4100,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney maal ko (luteron sey) bachatey huye maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. aur jo shakhs apney ghar walon ka difaa kartey huye maara jaey, wo shaheed hai. aur jo shakhs apney Deen ki khatir maara jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai. aur jo shakhs apni jaan bachatey huye maara jaey, wo bhi shaheed hai."
4101,"Hazrat Abu-Jafar (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Suwed bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) key paas betha tha. unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney haq ki khatir (ladtaa huwa) maara jaey, wo shaheed hai."
4102,"Hazrat ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs talwaar miyaan sey nikal kar logon par chalani shuru kar dey, us ka khoon zaya hai (us ka qatl jayez hai, uski koi diyat hogi na qisaas)."
4103,Abdur-Razzaaq sey bhi ye hadees inhi alfaz sey marwi hai magar us ney isey marfooa bayan nahin kiya.
4104,"Hazrat ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jisney (logon par) aslaha soonta, phir usey chalaanaa shuru kar diya to us ka khoon zaya hai (koi moawza hoga na us ka qisaas hi liya jaeyga)"
4105,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hum (musalmanon) par hathiyar uthaey, wo hum mein sey nahin."
4106,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney, jab wo Yamen key haakim they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein kuchh sona bheja jo abhi mitti sey alag nahin kiya gaya tha. aap ney wo sara sona taqseem farma diya, Aqra bin Habis Hanzali ko, jo ke banu Majaashea' sey they, Uena bin Badr Fazaari ko, Alqama bin Ulaasa Aamiri ko, jo ke banu Kilaab mein sey tha aur Zaid Taai ko jo ke banu Nabhaan mein sey tha. is baat sey Quraish aur Ansaar ko ghussa aa gaya. wo kehney lagey : aap Najdi sardaron ko dey rahey hain aur hamein chhod rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : main un ki taaleefe-qalb karta hun. itney main eik aadmi aaya jiski aankhen andar ko dhansi hui, rukhsaar ubhrey huye, dadhi ghani aur sar mundaa huwa tha, wo kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! Allah sey dar. aap ney farmaya : agar main hi Allah ka nafarman hun to kon Allah ki itaat kerega? us (Allah taalaa) ney to mujhey zamin walon par ameen banaya hai (tabhi to mujhey nabuwat sey sarfaraaz farmaya hai) lekin tum mujhey amanat-daar nahin samajhtey? chunanche haazirin mein sey eik shakhs ney uskey qatl ki ijazat talab ki lekin aap ney ijazat na di. jab wo aadmi chala gaya to aap ney farmaya : uski nasal sey kuchh aisey log namoodaar hongey jo Quran padhengey magar wo unkey halaq sey nichey nahin jaeyga. Deen sey is tarah saaf nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer apney shikar sey saaf nikal jata hai. wo musalmanon ko qatl kerengey. but paraston ko kuchh nahin kahengey. (Allah ki qism !) agar mainey unhen paya to unhen qome-Aad ki tarah qatl kar dunga."
4107,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : aakhir zamaney mein kuchh nau-umar, kam aql log zahir hongey. wo makhluq mein sey behtareen shakhs (Hazrat Muhammad Mustafa (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki baaten kerengey. unka eman unkey halaq sey tajawuz nahin kerega (aagey nahi badhega). Deen sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah shikar (key jism) sey teer (saaf) nikal jata hai. jab tumhari un sey mulaqat ho to unhen (be-daregh) qatl karo kyonkey unka qatl, qatl karney waley key liye qiyamat key ajr aur sawab ka zariya hoga."
4108,"Hazrat Shareek bin Shahaab sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke meri khahish thi ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum mein sey kisi ko miloon aur un sey khaarijiyon key barey mein poochhun, chunanche Eid-Mubarak key din Hazrat Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) key sath meri mulaqat hui. unkey sath unkey kuchh sathi bhi they. mainey un sey kaha : aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko khaarijiyon ka zikr farmatey suna hai? unhoney farmaya : haan ! mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (key farman) ko apney kanon sey suna aur mainey (us waqt ) aap ko apni aakhon sey dekha ke aap key paas kuchh maal laya gaya. aap ney usey taqseem farma diya. apni daeyn baain taraf waley logon ko diya lekin apney peechhey waley logon ko kuchh na diya. aap key peechhey sey eik aadmi khada huwa aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! aap ney taqseem mein insaf nahin kiya. wo aadmi kaley rang ka, mundey huye sar wala tha. is par do safed kapdey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (ye sun kar) shadeed ghussa aaya aur aap ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! tum merey baad koi aadmi mujh sey badh kar insaf karney wala nahin paogey. phir farmaya : akheer zamaney mein aisey log zahir hongey, aur ye bhi mujhey unhi sey lagta hai, jo Quran padhengey, magar wo unkey halaq sey nichey nahin utreyga. wo Islam sey is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer apney shikar sey (saaf) nikal jata hai. unkey khususi alamat sar mundwanaa hai. wo log hamesha (bar-bar) nikaltey rahengey yahan tak ke un mein sey aakhiri giroh Masih-Dajjaal key sath nikleyga. jab tum un sey milo to unhen (nisankoch) qatl karo. wo tamam makhluqat mein sey bad-tareen log hain. Imam Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke Shareek bin Shahaab (Hadees key raawi) koi maroof aadmi nahin. (balke majhool hai kyonkey Azraq bin Qais key ilawa dusrey kisi shakhs ney is sey riwayat bayan nahin ki.)"
4109,Hazrat Saad bin Abu Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman sey ladna kufr aur usey gaali dena fisq (kabeera gunah) hai.
4110,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq aur us sey ladaai ladna kufr hai.
4111,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq (kabeera gunah) hai aur us sey ladna kufr hai. Aban ney (Abu Is-haq sey) puchha : Abu Is-haq ! aap ney ye hadees sirf Abul Aehwas sey suni hai? unhoney kaha : (nahin) balke Aswad aur Hubaira sey bhi mainey ye hadees suni hai.
4112,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya musalman ko gaali dena fisq aur us sey ladaai ladna kufr hai.
4113,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq hai aur us sey ladaai karna kufr hai.
4114,Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali galoch karna fisq aur us sey ladaai ladna kufr hai. (Imam Shoba ney apney ustaad Hammad sey kaha : ) tum kis par tohmat lagatey ho? kya tum Mansoor par tohmat lagatey ho? kya tum Zubaida par tohmat lagatey ho? kya tum Suleman (Alaihissalam) par tohmat lagatey ho? Hammad ney kaha : nahin (main un mein sey kisi par bhi tohmat nahin lagata) lekin main (in sab key ustaad) Abu-Waeil par tohmat lagata hun. (ke aaya us ney Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees suni hai ya nahin.)
4115,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ka gaali dena fisq aur us ka (dusrey musalmanon sey) ladaai karna kufr hai. Zubaida kehtey hain : mainey Abu-Waeil sey puchha : kya aap ney is hadees ko Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna hai? unhoney farmaya : haan ! (suna hai).
4116,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq aur us sey ladaai ladna kufr hai.
4117,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : musalman ko gaali dena fisq (nafarmani) aur us sey ladaai ladna kufr hai.
4118,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : momin sey ladaai ladna kufr aur us ko gaali dena fisq (Allah ki nafarmaani) hai.
4119,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (tasleem shuda ameer ki) itaat sey nikal jaey aur jamaat sey juda ho jaey, agar wo usi haal mein mara to jahiliyat ki maut mara. jo shakhs meri ummat key khilaf (hathiyar band ho kar) nikla aur har nek aur bad ko bila imtiyaaz (farq kiye) qatl karney laga, wo na momin ki parwa karta hai na kisi zimmi key ehad ka lihaz rakhta hai to us ka mujh sey koi talluq nahin. aur jo shakhs (kisi qism key hizbi, qaumi ya mazhabi aur garohi ta'ssub mein aa kar) kisi mubham aur andhey jhandey key nichey ladaa, kisi eik jamaat ki taraf dawat deta hai ya kisi jamaat ki khatir wo ghussey mein aa kar ladtaa hai aur maara jata hai to uski maut jahiliyat ki maut hogi."
4120,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs (andha dhund ta'ssub mein aa kar) kisi mubham (poshida) aur andhey jhandey key tehat ladaa, wo sirf apney giroh ki himayat mein ladtaa aur usi ki himayat mein ghazab-naak hota hai, (woh maara jaey) to uski maut jahiliyat ki (haram) maut hogi. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke (is hadees ka raawi) Imran Al Qattan qawi nahin hai."
4121,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi musalman apney bhai ki taraf aslahey key sath ishara karey (eik musalman dusrey par hathiyar utha ley aur doosra bhi utha ley) to wo dono jahannam key kinarey par hotey hain. aur jab eik, dusrey ko qatl kar dey to dono ikhattey jahannam mein gir padtey hain."
4122,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke jab do musalman eik dusrey par aslahey key sath hamla keren, wo dono jahannam key kinarey par hotey hain. phir jab un mein sey koi eik , dusrey ko qatl kar deta hai to dono aag mein jatey hain (qatil to musalman ko qatl karney ki wajeh sey aur maqtool is liye ke uski niyat bhi musalman ko qatl karney hi ki thi)."
4123,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman apni talwaarein ley kar eik dusrey key muqabil aa jaeyn, phir un mein sey eik dusrey ko qatl kar dey to wo dono jahannam mein jaeyngey. puchha gaya : Allah key Rasool ! qatil ka jahannam mein jana to samajh mein aata hai magar maqtool key jahannam mein janey ki wajeh kya hai? aap ney farmaya is ka irada bhi apney sathi ko qatl karney ka tha."
4124,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman apni talwaaren ley kar eik dusrey key muqabil aa jaeyn, phir un mein sey koi dusrey ko qatl kar dey to wo dono aag mein jaeyngey. ye riwayat bhi bilkul pehli riwayat ki tarah hai."
4125,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman apni talwaaren ley kar aamney samney aa jaeyn jabkey un mein sey har eik, dusrey ko qatl karna chahta ho (phir chahey koi kisi ko qatl kar dey) to dono aag mein jaeyngey. puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! qatil to theek hai magar maqtool kyon? aap ney farmaya : wo bhi apney sathi ko qatl kerna chaahta tha."
4126,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman talwaaren ley kar muqabla karney lagen, phir un mein sey eik dusrey ko qatl kar dey to qatil aur maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey."
4127,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jab do musalman apni talwaaren (ya koi bhi aslaha) ley kar aamney samney aa jaeyn, phir un mein sey eik dusrey ko qatl kar dey to qatil aur maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey. sahaba ney arz kiya : qatil to jahannam mein jaey magar maqtool kyon? aap ney farmaya is ney bhi to apney sathi ko qatl karney ka irada kiya tha."
4128,"Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman talwaaren ley kar eik dusrey sey ladney lagen, phir un mein sey eik dusrey ko maar dey to qatil aur maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey."
4129,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab do musalman talwaaron sey lais ho kar eik, dusrey key aamney samney aajaeyn (aur ladney lagen), phir un mein sey eik, dusrey ko qatl kar dey (ya dono eik dusrey ko qatl kar den) to qatil aur maqtool dono aag mein jaeyngey. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool qatil ka jahannam mein jana to sahih hai magar maqtool kyon aag mein jaeyga? aap ney farmaya, us ka irada bhi apney sathi ko qatl karney hi ka tha."
4130,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad kafir na ban jana ke eik dusrey ki gardanen kaatney lago.
4131,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad kafir na ban jana ke eik dusrey ki gardanen kaatney lag jao. kisi shakhs ko uskey baap ya bhai key jurm mein na pakda jaeyga. Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye (mazkura riwayat muttasil bayan karna) ghalat hai. durust (ye hai ke ye) riwayat mursal hai.
4132,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad kafir na ban jana ke eik dusrey ki gardanen utaarney lago. kisi aadmi ko uskey baap ya bhai key jurm mein nahin pakda ja sakta.
4133,Hazrat Masruq sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main tumhen is haal mein na paoon ke tum merey baad kafir ban jao aur eik dusrey ki gardanen kaato. kisi shakhs ko uskey baap ya bhai key jurm mein giraftar na kiya jaeyga. ye (mursal riwayat ki nisbat) durust hai.
4134,Hazrat Masruq sey manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad kafir na ban jao. (ye riwayat ) mursal hai (aur yehi sahih hai).
4135,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : merey baad gumrah na ban jana ke eik dusrey ki gardanen kaatney lago.
4136,Hazrat Jareer (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Hajjatul-wadaa key din logon ko chup karaya aur farmaya : merey baad kafir na ban jana ke eik dusrey ki gardanen utaarney lago.
4137,Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah Bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : logon ko chup karao. phir aap ney farmaya : (aey logo ! ) tumhein musalman dekhney key baad main tumhen is haal mein na paoon ke tum merey baad kafir ban jao aur eik dusrey ki gardanen kaatney lago.
